sentences: Her collaborative experiences include performances with violinists Mark Kaplan, Ilya Kaler, Jaako Kuusisto, Robin Sharp, Barnabas Keleman, Richard Lin, violists Atar Arad, Yuval Gotlibovich, and cellist Csaba Onczay.
She has also appeared under conductor Irwin Hoffman.
Her principal teachers include Lev Vlassenko and Luba Edlina-Dubinsky.
